This paper deals with anomaly detection in a Cyber-Physical System (CPS) using unsupervised machine learning. The paper discusses the use of Deep Neural Networks (DNN) and Support Vector Machines (SVM) for this purpose. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
